premise_source_doc_sentence: After the war the USAF reviewed its figures in an investigation code-named Sabre Measure Charlie and downgraded the kill ratio of the North American F-86 Sabre against the Mikoyan-Gurevich MiG-15 by half from 14:1 to 7:1 .
Kill Ratio is a 2016 American action-thriller film directed by Paul Tanter .

In early combat operations , the Zero gained a legendary reputation as a dogfighter , achieving an outstanding kill ratio of 12 to 1 , but by mid-1942 a combination of new tactics and the introduction of better equipment enabled Allied pilots to engage the Zero on generally equal terms .
However , Soviet kill claims were also highly exaggerated , based upon inherent flaws in their film grading procedures .
